\ls4\ilvl0
\f1\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 >= $100
\f0\b0  \uc0\u8594  an LLM 
\f3\fs26 review_agent
\f0\fs24  analyzes risk, then a human-in-the-loop node pauses the workflow for a human via ADK 2.0's 
\f3\fs26 RequestInput
\f0\fs24 .\
