\f1\b security screen
\f0\b0  node into our ADK workflow. This checkpoint executes 
\f2\i before the LLM
\f0\i0  for any expense over $100. It masks PII in real time and immediately short-circuits detected injection attempts directly to human review, completely bypassing the LLM.\
